                                </p>    
                            </div>
                            <div class="space-y-2 sm:space-y-3 mb-6 sm:mb-8">
                                <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center space-x-2 sm:space-x-3">
                                    <span class="text-foreground text-sm sm:text-base">Complete 5-minute personalized quiz</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center space-x-2 sm:space-x-3">
                                    <span class="text-foreground text-sm sm:text-base">Get AI-powered therapist recommendations</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center space-x-2 sm:space-x-3">
                                    <span class="text-foreground text-sm sm:text-base">Filter by location, price and specialty</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center space-x-2 sm:space-x-3">
                                    <span class="text-foreground text-sm sm:text-base">Read verified reviews from real clients</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center space-x-2 sm:space-x-3">
                                    <span class="text-foreground text-sm sm:text-base">View therapist credentials and recommendations</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-linear-to-br from-primary/5 to-primary/10 p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-12 flex items-center">
                            <div class="w-full">
                                <div class="bg-muted/30 rounded-lg p-2 sm:p-4 space-y-2 sm:space-y-3">
                                    <img class="w-full rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl h-50 sm:h-62.5 object-cover" alt="Search" loading="lazy" width="400" height="250" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" style="color: transparent;" src="https://pbs.twimg.com/amplify_video_thumb/1962091061205155841/img/1l--dmZ2C_YOiptG.jpg">
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 bg-white rounded-lg p-2 sm:p-3 shadow-sm">
                                    <span class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-muted-foreground">Search: "Reiki therapist near me"</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="space-y-0.5">
                                    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-2.5 shadow-sm flex items-center space-x-3">
                                        <div class="flex-1">
                                            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                                                <span class="text-sm font-medium">Dr.Sofia Mendes</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground">
                                                <span>Holistic Massage</span>
                                                <span>4.9 estrelas</span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <span class="text-sm font-medium text-primary">65€</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-2.5 shadow-sm flex items-center space-x-3">
                                        <div class="flex-1">
                                            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                                                <span class="text-sm font-medium">Miguel Torres</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground">
                                                <span>Reiki Master</span>
                                                <span>4.8 estrelas</span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <span class="text-sm font-medium text-primary">55€</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-2.5 shadow-sm flex items-center space-x-3">
                                        <div class="flex-1">
                                            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                                                <span class="text-sm font-medium">Ana Rodrigues</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground">
                                                <span>Meditation Coach</span>
                                                <span>5 estrelas</span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <span class="text-sm font-medium text-primary">65€</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-16 text-center">
                <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-8 opacity-70">
                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                        <span class="text-muted-foreground">Certified Professionals</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                        <span class="text-muted-foreground">Secure Payments</span>
